name: Hina Inu
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Hina Inu ($HINA) is a fully decentralized, peer-to-peer deflationary community token that passively rewards its holders with a 2% tax redistribution for all transactions.

$HINA is currently on a mission to form the largest INU ecosystem dubbed “Super Pack”, where INU tokens will come together to create a united NFT marketplace and staking platform.
